{"tid":1563306,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有關美國因為香港人唔唱美國歌家而唔幫香港人","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:54:31.000Z","uid":287745,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"277146e125a3396b356682ad2c9db6cb2beb193a","tid":1563306,"uid":287745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:51:56.000Z","msg":"係今日國際政治角力形勢下，美中矛盾愈演愈烈，Trump拎香港做一個籌碼，係各取所需嘅心態，香港人向民主世界求救，美國為左鞏固地位、Trump又借機拎到選民支持連任，形勢係咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n但民主無論點都好，都必定需要自己去爭取甚至係打返黎，而唔應該係一味靠哂人，甚者，更加唔應該係向別人乞求，而連登有聲音係叫人咪唱自己首歌，唱人地國家，完全給予人一個好肉酸嘅感覺。呢家香港人係為左爭取民主，與全世界民主國家日聯結，包括美國，老實講對於美國人黎講我地更似係一場電視，正義同邪惡之爭，佢地支持我地，唔會係因為我地乞求。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家對於美國真係好似藍絲宣傳咁係主人唔敢得失，唱少兩次美國國歌都要屌架話，我地根本無令美國人或西方人動容嘅個種追求民主、公義之精神，無疑只會係自毀城牆。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美港係盟友，而唔係主僕</span></span></strong>。"},{"pid":"da641a9c6ae8a25eb5f07a8616ec36e0b3030d92","tid":1563306,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:52:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ceb1141cd4ba01b48d70daf0705b397f18b2be6","tid":1563306,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:53:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7f93ed3d1299f3f39d68b06c92084bf2fe094f19","ti